Start app with Username/Password fields and Login/Register buttons
    Register simply checks for duplicate usernames and adds record to file
    Login checks for username and compares hashed password - Password is hashed
    by client before being sent to server over the socket
Once Login is verified, show single pane for Buddy List
Buddy list has your username at the top, with a Broadcast button, a Logout
button, a History button, and a list of other online users
Clicking the Broadcast button or double clicking any of the users opens a
Chat Pane
The Chat Pane shows either Broadcast or Recipient at the top, with a chat
history text area, with a text field and Send button at the bottom
You can have multiple Chat panes open
